values:
Hello all.

This journal is friends only.  If you want to be added, just reply and tell me why in 500 words or less.  Those with good spelling, punctuation, and grammar have a good chance of getting added, as well as those who I know in Real Life.

All entries following this one will be friends only.  There will be absolutely no exceptions.

<strike>Sorry</strike> for any inconvience this creates.
